{"tid":813680,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]大家接唔接受到餐牌寫 豬扒 黎到變 火腿?","createTime":"2018-09-10T15:42:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T16:51:18.000Z","uid":147017,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c399c3a17091f73e7c2a251dc4fbffcc45b8eff1","tid":813680,"uid":147017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:42:49.000Z","msg":"今日去左一間旺角既&quot;台X餐廳&quot;﹐食晚飯。叫芝士吉列豬扒飯﹐第一啖咬落去已經覺得奇怪﹐完全無豬扒口感。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/232705_ebe806122f2c563a0d21466638411349.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F232705_ebe806122f2c563a0d21466638411349.jpeg&h=a9ba2690&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再望一望,火腿黎。檢查哂成舊吉列芝士豬扒(火腿),得炸粉﹐芝士同火腿。<br />\n呢一刻我壞疑待應落錯單﹐再檢查餐牌。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/232706_0161bfda3c04b0f98ae9115a2eebb309.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F232706_0161bfda3c04b0f98ae9115a2eebb309.jpeg&h=9753642f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係無吉列芝士火腿飯。<br />\n<br />\n雖然個飯唔貴﹐但有種被騙既感覺。<br />\n<br />\n大家接唔接受到餐牌寫 豬扒 之後變 火腿?"},{"pid":"cddb8ab33c1eb4d4137dd9b2baf7080b39b55bef","tid":813680,"uid":40140,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:44:08.000Z","msg":"唔出聲？"},{"pid":"b3c053e7d5a99e6cb54416a4449fedebdadeb950","tid":813680,"uid":208726,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:45:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9ed4dfe535397a66c9e417ec41868247cc87cc0","tid":813680,"uid":63202,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:45:23.000Z","msg":"你自己都唔出聲就唔好諗住我地外人會幫你公審佢啦🤔"},{"pid":"d853d379d7b19c275277933a85bb6e09baebbd7f","tid":813680,"uid":147017,"like":0,"dislike":30,"score":-30,"quote":{"pid":"cddb8ab33c1eb4d4137dd9b2baf7080b39b55bef","tid":813680,"uid":40140,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:44:08.000Z","ms